{"tid":2110640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「除低口罩係最危險嘅時候」 袁國勇籲留家用膳助醫護","createTime":"2020-07-16T05:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T11:42:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04485ef8af95f158d54103baff59be04011a5277","tid":2110640,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"「除低口罩係最危險嘅時候」<br />\n袁國勇籲留家用膳助醫護<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/HV6BYML4HHILQGYUKST2QWUCYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FHV6BYML4HHILQGYUKST2QWUCYQ%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3x1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=8a7174f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FHV6BYML4HHILQGYUKST2QWUCYQ%2F&h=ed118c5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/HV6BYML4HHILQGYUKST2QWUCYQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇籲留家用膳助醫護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BI5UzRdppfNvslQqqVpZBtZXbLc=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3UVGNBUO5EOSPXEVGTDCJOQX6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBI5UzRdppfNvslQqqVpZBtZXbLc%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3UVGNBUO5EOSPXEVGTDCJOQX6Y.jpg&h=b5a81c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有微生物學系專家表示，社區爆發已無法控制，呼籲公眾切勿外出用膳，盡量留家用膳或轉為外賣，<span class=\"orange\">「除低口罩係最危險嘅時候」</span>。同時，專家警告港人要全面抗疫，將社區疫情壓下來，否則社區很快全面失守，醫院或會逐步癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：撤關稅寬免勢打擊轉口地位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何栢良：須中斷食肆傳播鏈<br />\n<br />\n港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇（圖）昨日在港台節目中表示，3月中時已有研究顯示病毒有變種情況，但由於當時防疫措施嚴謹，因此未有大規模爆發。然而，<span class=\"orange\">本港限制措施在父親節後似乎完全放寬，口水及飛沫在食肆傳播有很大問題，尤其食肆及酒吧的空氣流量很低，因而引發新一波疫情。</span><br />\n<br />\n袁國勇續指，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇稱明白餐飲業界的經營困難，但如果本港不能將疫情控制下來，可能造成醫院爆發，甚至有醫護人員受感染，屆時醫院便會逐漸癱瘓。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在商台。。。。。。。。。。。。7月5日至前日本地確診個案，已經超越3月數字，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"4ff0ddec352b96b62528aabf25b44349abaaf37e","tid":2110640,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfe2dcf5093dd4fa8845e11ea3f884fc6fc80e8","tid":2110640,"uid":168492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"那些上夜班的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aeb035c554543bcb2e2e53e7f3ad60cf4df6759","tid":2110640,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"咁仲番唔番工？"},{"pid":"74e581dfc1e9b9059ec835961f6c62cb9eb45b8e","tid":2110640,"uid":134012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"唔返工你養我？"},{"pid":"d1acb970f898fb056eb33aa440fa9fe9c485959a","tid":2110640,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:45:26.000Z","msg":"借個位 保安局發出超過20萬張豁免強制檢疫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2106369/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2106369/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家支持廣傳消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔自救大家玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我哋可以做咩嘢？</span></span></strong><br />\n1.話比身邊嘅人知香港有個後門大量吸收潛在冇病症感染者及傳播者。<br />\n<br />\n2.呼籲身邊所有人戴口罩，特別係果班唔肯帶嘅中年人<br />\n<br />\n3.如果身邊有料，可以報上傳媒比如蘋果。<br />\n例如喺之前post有其他人話知道：<br />\n灣仔入境個邊D移民公司而家當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n4.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹各自爬山 他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fce86dd468186fa1e4de8f886cd598471426e3","tid":2110640,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"Office丶公園食飯就安全？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5b96b3cbecdcb0d7968672a757c5765a6945a4","tid":2110640,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:33:20.000Z","msg":"老細  預返D時間比我返屋企食飯OK? 一陣返!"},{"pid":"e9d2569bc698e67cb4cb5a00f98f34d4bc010940","tid":2110640,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"wfh"}]}